_sText: CT-team must escort very important person to the nearest rescue site before Terrorists can assasinate him. There are 2 rescuezones available. Created by ICS 27th of October 2008 E-mail: ics@ics-base.net WWW: http://www.ics-base.net This is VIP version (assassination) of my previous map de_hiekka. It has been improved since and 90% of the textures have been changed, more routes added to support assasination mode better and some minor fixes. The defuse verion can be found from here I decited to make vip-mod version of the map since there arent any good big ones available - or not even smaller ones. I looked the assasination section and it is quite empty. The reason why i made it so different looking is that players can easily spot which version they play. Have fun! PS: Hiekka is a finnish word and translates as sand in english.
